title: House fires: financial help and fire safety

heading_context: House fires: financial help and fire safety
chunks.html_content: The Red Cross and your local council can help with accommodation and other needs in an emergency.
chunks.plain_content:
House fires: financial help and fire safety
The Red Cross and your local council can help with accommodation and other needs in an emergency.

heading_context: House fires: financial help and fire safety
chunks.html_content: Contact the Red Cross for emergency help with accommodation, clothing, food etc as well as help dealing with insurance companies.
chunks.plain_content:
House fires: financial help and fire safety
Emergency help
Contact the Red Cross for emergency help with accommodation, clothing, food etc as well as help dealing with insurance companies.

heading_context: House fires: financial help and fire safety
If you have nowhere to stay
chunks.html_content: Contact your local council. They may be able to help you with emergency housing.
chunks.plain_content:

heading_context: House fires: financial help and fire safety
chunks.html_content: Get fire safety advice on the Fire Kills page, including information on smoke alarms, making your home safe and help for people with disabilities.
